                    <tr>
                        <td valign="top" style="padding: 0px 10px;">
                            <div style="font-size: 15px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">
                                <br/>
                                Dear  <t t-out="object.name or ''"> Applicant Name</t>,
                                <br/><br/>
                                We are thrilled to extend our warmest congratulations on your well-deserved appraisal. Your hard work, dedication, and outstanding performance have not gone unnoticed, and we are delighted to recognize your contributions to the team.
                                <br/><br/>
