                                <br/><br/>
                                Should you have any questions or require further clarification regarding the contents of the appraisal letter, please feel free to reach out to the HR department or your supervisor.
                                <br/><br/>
                                Once again, congratulations on this significant achievement. We value your continued dedication to our team and look forward to witnessing your continued success.
                                <br/><br/>
                            </div>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
            </field>
            <field name="auto_delete" eval="True"/>
        </record>

